The Shutter Teste is designed for the 4" screen specified in the parts document.

Other screens are NOT supported.

A few builders have not been able to get the specified 4" screen in their country and instead have used a smaller 3.5" screen 
which has the same tft and touch drivers and resolution as the 4" screen.

The file TheShutterTester3_5_screen.3mf in this folder is a sligghtly modified version of the orginal, having a smaller aperture to fit the smaller screen.

The file TheShutterTester_tft_exp_frame_3_5.3mf is a slightly modified version of the original, 
having the holes/standoffs moved to align with the fixing holes of the smaller tft screen,

The mounting hole spacing is 92mm x 49.5mm.

Other parts, (bottom & back) are the same as the 4" case and the print files will be found there

There are of course different 3.5" screens available. The 3d print files are made to fit one particular screen,
photos of which are in ther photos folder.

Note: The screen display is rotated 180 degress compared to the 4" screen, so when mounting, the connextion pins should be at the botom of the screen.

Note: IMPORTANT this 3.5" screen is NOT supported. Whilst my 3.5" screen worked fine, as has another builders, another screen was found to have black/white inverted. 
If this is a fault of the screen or a different varient is unknown.
